    "settings.ai.volc.header": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "火山引擎 / Volcengine"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "火山引擎 / Volcengine"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "settings.ai.volc.help": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Get an API Key at https://console.volcengine.com/ark/region:ark+cn-beijing/apiKey (Volcengine Ark console → API Key management → Create).\nSet \"Model\" to either a model name (e.g. doubao-seed-1-6-250615) or the inference endpoint ID (e.g. ep-2025xxxx-xxxxx) — find it under \"Online Inference / Endpoint\" in the console.\nEndpoint defaults to the official Volcengine URL — change it to your URL if you use an OpenAI-compatible relay.\n⚠️ Key is stored as **plain text** in the prefs plist (deliberate trade-off for single-user dev builds)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "到 https://console.volcengine.com/ark/region:ark+cn-beijing/apiKey 申请 API Key(火山方舟控制台 → API Key 管理 → 创建)。\nModel 字段填 model 名(如 doubao-seed-1-6-250615)或推理接入点 endpoint ID(如 ep-2025xxxx-xxxxx)—— 在「在线推理 / 推理接入点」里能拿到。\nEndpoint 默认是火山方舟官方;用第三方 OpenAI 兼容中转站把它改成你的 URL。\n⚠️ Key 以**明文**保存在偏好设置 plist 里(单 Mac 个人 dev 版的取舍)。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "settings.ai.volc.inputPrice.label": {
      "comment": "Phase 107: Label for volcengine input token price field (CNY per million tokens).",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
