          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.1": {
      "comment": "J-type humorous quote shown in status bar.",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Plans can't outpace change — but yours come pretty close."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "计划赶不上变化,但你的计划比变化还快。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.10": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Anxiety fuels J-types. Output is the byproduct."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "焦虑是 J 人的燃料,效率是燃烧后的产物。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.11": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Your to-do list isn't \"to-do.\" It's \"to-control.\""
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你的 to-do 不是 to-do,是 to-control。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.12": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Everything has a home. That's the ritual."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "每件东西都有家,这就是 J 人的仪式感。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.13": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Desk neatness = mental order. Both directions."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "桌面整洁度 = 内心秩序值,两个方向都成立。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.14": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Being J isn't fate — it's daily compound interest."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "做 J 人不是命运,是日复一日的复利。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.15": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Close your eyes — can you list what's on your desk? Real J-types can."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "闭眼回想桌上有什么 —— 数得清才算够 J。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.16": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The joy of finding something is the echo of nearly losing it."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "找到的快乐,源于失而复得的瞬间。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.17": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "We don't forget our things — we forget to tell ourselves where they are."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "人不会忘记物品,只是忘了告诉自己放在哪。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.18": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A home isn't where things are piled — it's where you know they are."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "家不是堆东西的地方,是知道东西在哪的地方。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.19": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "One quick note beats one long night of searching."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "记一条,胜过翻一夜。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.2": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You're not a control freak. You're \"organized.\""
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你不是控制狂,你叫「井井有条」。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.20": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Order isn't a tic — it's tomorrow, given back to you."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "秩序不是洁癖,是省下来的明天。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.21": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Objects don't get lost — we just forget the path."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "物品自己不会迷路,是你忘了路。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.22": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Chaos is free. Order is a gift you give yourself."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "混乱是免费的,整理是给自己的一份心意。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.23": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Future-you will thank present-you for writing the address down."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "未来的你,会感谢现在写下位置的你。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.24": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Between you and chaos lies a single coordinate."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你与混乱之间,只差一个坐标。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.25": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Write it down, and the world gains an index."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "记下来,世界就有了索引。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.26": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Where tidiness ends, calm begins."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "整理的尽头,是宁静。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.27": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Only what you can find truly belongs to you."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "能找到的东西,才真正属于你。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.28": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Things go missing. Records don't."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "东西会丢,记录不会。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.29": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Knowing where it is is its own kind of safety."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "位置感,即安全感。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.3": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "If finding it takes more than 30 seconds, log it."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "找东西超过 30 秒,就该录进这个 app。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.30": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tidiness is one way of being kind to yourself."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "整理,也是一种善待自己。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.31": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "J-types don't fear chaos — they prevent it ahead of time."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "J 人不焦虑混乱,因为他们提前预防。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.32": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Order starts small — with one object at a time."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "秩序由小事开始,从一件物品开始。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.33": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Your room is the hard drive of your mind."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你的房间,就是你大脑的硬盘。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.34": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "What matters most deserves a name and a home."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "越是重要的东西,越值得有名字和家。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.35": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Searching shouldn't be daily. It should be the exception."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "找东西不该是日常,而该是例外。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.4": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Not putting it back means deciding twice. J-type forbidden."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "不放回去等于再决策一次,J 人禁忌。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.5": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Empty to-do list: peak dopamine."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "清空待办那一刻,就是多巴胺峰值。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.6": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You're not forgetful. You set checkpoints for future-you."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你不是健忘,是给未来的自己设了 checkpoint。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.7": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Organizing = making decisions in advance."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "整理的本质,是把决策提前。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.8": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Mystery objects in a drawer? An insult to your J-type honor."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "抽屉里有不知名物件?这是对 J 人身份的侮辱。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.jquote.9": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Procrastination is a P-type luxury. You don't qualify."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "拖延是 P 人的特权,你没这个资格。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "status.summary.days %lld": {
      "comment": "Status bar: days used since first launch.",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "variations": {
